Maintainer: Darian Lanx <dmalloc@users.sourceforge.net>
BuildDepends: glib2-dev, gdbm3, libiconv-dev, libgettext3-dev, libgpg-error, pth2-dev, gnupg2, fink (>= 0.24.12)
